<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<ContentPage
    xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui"
    xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml"
    x:Class="MAUI_PROJECT_PDM.Views.AboutUs"
    Title="AboutUs"
    BackgroundColor="#EEE">
    <ScrollView>
        <VerticalStackLayout
            MaximumWidthRequest="400"
            HorizontalOptions="CenterAndExpand"
            VerticalOptions="CenterAndExpand">
            <Image
                MaximumWidthRequest="300"
                Source="omnifood_logo.png"
                Margin="0, 20, 0, 20" />

            <Label
                TextColor="Black"
                FontSize="Body"
                Padding="0, 10, 0, 10">
                <Label.Text>
                    At Omnifood, we are a passionate team of food enthusiasts and developers dedicated to making healthy eating easy and enjoyable for everyone. Our app is designed to help you plan and organize your meals based on your dietary preferences, with accurate calorie and nutritional information to help you make informed choices about what you're eating.
                </Label.Text>
            </Label>
            <Label
                TextColor="Black"
                FontSize="Body"
                Padding="0, 0, 0, 10">
                <Label.Text>
                    With our customizable meal plans and recipe collection, you can easily find delicious and healthy meals that fit your lifestyle. Whether you're a vegan, meat-based or fish-based eater, our app offers a wide range of options to choose from.
                </Label.Text>
            </Label>
            <Label
                TextColor="Black"
                FontSize="Body"
                Padding="0, 0, 0, 10">
                <Label.Text>
                    At Omnifood, we believe that healthy eating should be easy and accessible to everyone, which is why our app is designed to be user-friendly and intuitive. Our team of experienced developers and nutrition experts are committed to providing you with the best possible user experience and regularly update the app with new features to enhance your experience.
                </Label.Text>
            </Label>
            <Label
                TextColor="Black"
                FontSize="Body"
                Padding="0, 0, 0, 10">
                <Label.Text>
                    By using our app, you'll be able to easily track your calorie intake, stay on top of your nutritional goals, and make healthy eating a part of your everyday routine. Join us on our journey to healthy living and let's make nutritious eating easy and enjoyable for everyone!
                </Label.Text>
            </Label>
            <Label
                TextColor="Black"
                FontSize="Body">
                <Label.Text>
                    Our team is based in the heart of Bucharest, at Strada General Berthelot, Nr. 9, Sector 1, Romania. We are proud to serve customers around the world who are committed to making healthy eating a part of their lifestyle. Join us on our journey to healthy living and let's make nutritious eating easy and enjoyable for everyone!
                </Label.Text>
            </Label>

            <Label
                TextColor="Black"
                FontSize="Body"
                HorizontalTextAlignment="Center"
                Margin="0, 100, 0, 0">
                <Label.Text>
                    Copyright @Omnifood app
                </Label.Text>
            </Label>


        </VerticalStackLayout>
    </ScrollView>
</ContentPage>